{
  "id": "RAW_9db9cc4d",
  "title": "图灵奖得主杨立昆：谁将是人工智能的受益者？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NzY4MzQyMQ==&mid=2650151267&idx=1&sn=b42b179e3b99b4b6bb90b0bb5dd0e4ce",
  "date": "2026-04-03 00:00:00",
  "author": "哈佛商业评论",
  "siteName": "哈佛商业评论",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c6845254&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FBiawCOWWXNbQuvIpRtgdyhKB6OxYc50Yn6O5hLicgPbiaF8hib2a79VicwYehmaMjr0OtNQdZzX4XyNC51cMntDk8BJc41Cv5ZzgOOocW3lNNWNE%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mn71tj9h15zu\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">人工智能引发了一系列的问题。它改变了社会，引起了经济变革，如同其他任何一项技术革命一样，它也创造了新的职业并使一些职业消失。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">谁将是其中的受益者呢？</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mn71zou4wp7\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <div data-tools=\"新媒体排版\" data-id=\"2926887\" data-style-type=\"undefined\" data-xmt-x1=\"621.5\" data-xmt-y1=\"4257.734375\" data-xmt-x2=\"1298.5\" data-xmt-y2=\"4291.734375\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:17px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div data-xmt-x1=\"621.5\" data-xmt-y1=\"4257.734375\" data-xmt-x2=\"1298.5\" data-xmt-y2=\"4291.734375\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" data-xmt-x1=\"621.5\" data-xmt-y1=\"4257.734375\" data-xmt-x2=\"1298.5\" data-xmt-y2=\"4291.734375\" style=\"transform: rotate(0deg);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div data-xmt-x1=\"621.5\" data-xmt-y1=\"4257.734375\" data-xmt-x2=\"1298.5\" data-xmt-y2=\"4291.734375\" style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"padding-left: 6px;display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div data-xmt-x1=\"869.109375\" data-xmt-y1=\"4264.734375\" data-xmt-x2=\"1044.875375\" data-xmt-y2=\"4291.734375\" style=\"padding-left:6px;font-size:17px;padding-right:6px;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p data-xmt-x1=\"875.109375\" data-xmt-y1=\"4264.734375\" data-xmt-x2=\"1050.875375\" data-xmt-y2=\"4291.734375\" style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">谁将从人工智能革命中受益？</span></strong></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mn71tj9hqvc\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">一些杰出经济学家将人工智能视为“通用技术”，认为它将在未来几十年中不断传播并深刻改变经济生活。我们在历史上创造的“通用技术”还有蒸汽机、电力、计算机等。像以前的技术变革一样，人工智能也将取代一些行业。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mn71tj9h1q8m\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">19世纪70年代时，法国有50%的人以农业为生，而这一比例在2019年降至5%。我们适应过时代，现在我们需要再次适应。部分就业人口的技能已无法应对社会的需要，他们必须接受新的职业培训以适应新的工作，或者由社会来接管他们。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mn71tj9hqvw\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">我担心目前这种进展的加速会导致越来越多的人失业，但是专门研究这些问题的经济学家给我吃了一颗定心丸。例如，麻省理工学院的埃里克·布林约尔松（Erik Brynjolfsson）和其他一些经济学家曾断言，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">“通用技术”渗透经济的速度会受到工人学习如何利用它所需时间的严格限制，这个过程需要15～20年。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mn71tj9h253k\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">我不确定人工智能革命是否会让所有人受益。深耕于有资质的、创新型的、专注于人际关系或人力资源职位的人更有可能保住工作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mn71tj9h1xl4\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">有一件事是可以确定的：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">人工智能及其应用无法参与竞争的东西会变得更有价值，这是已经得到证明的人类经验。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">自动化大幅度降低了制成品的价格，随着人工智能在工业界的渗透，这种趋势将会继续，甚至加剧，但是服务业、手工业和房地产业不会以相同的方式受到影响。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mn71tj9h8go\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">举个例子，我们每个人都可以花不到两欧元的低价或通过订阅的方式聆听最喜欢的音乐家的作品，然而如果要欣赏摇滚音乐会或歌剧，我们就需要支付50～300欧元。区别在于，独特的事物赋予了生命独特的时刻。一顿大餐，参观自然景点或博物馆，听一场爵士乐音乐会</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">ÿÿ</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">我因为能够做这些事情而感到高兴。我们越来越重视创造力和独到的体验，越来越不看重大众化的产品。在健康、艺术、科学、教育、体育等领域的职业中，感性的方面在未来将占有重要的一席之地。</span></span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mn71zvfb455\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <div data-tools=\"新媒体排版\" data-id=\"2926887\" data-style-type=\"undefined\" data-xmt-x1=\"621.5\" data-xmt-y1=\"4257.734375\" data-xmt-x2=\"1298.5\" data-xmt-y2=\"4291.734375\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:17px;text-align:justify;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div data-xmt-x1=\"621.5\" data-xmt-y1=\"4257.734375\" data-xmt-x2=\"1298.5\" data-xmt-y2=\"4291.734375\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" data-xmt-x1=\"621.5\" data-xmt-y1=\"4257.734375\" data-xmt-x2=\"1298.5\" data-xmt-y2=\"4291.734375\" style=\"transform: rotate(0deg);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div data-xmt-x1=\"621.5\" data-xmt-y1=\"4257.734375\" data-xmt-x2=\"1298.5\" data-xmt-y2=\"4291.734375\" style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <div style=\"padding-left: 6px;display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n         <div data-xmt-x1=\"869.109375\" data-xmt-y1=\"4264.734375\" data-xmt-x2=\"1044.875375\" data-xmt-y2=\"4291.734375\" style=\"padding-left:6px;font-size:17px;padding-right:6px;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p data-xmt-x1=\"875.109375\" data-xmt-y1=\"4264.734375\" data-xmt-x2=\"1050.875375\" data-xmt-y2=\"4291.734375\" style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;\"><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">如何解释人工智能？</span></strong></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mn71tj9hidb\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">一些悲观主义者认为深度学习系统是“黑匣子”，但他们错了。工程师可以深入检查神经网络的功能，包括所有的细节。诚然，当神经网络具有数百万个单位和数十亿个连接时，似乎很难完全理解它的每一个决策，但这不正是所有智能决策的特点吗？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mn71tj9h1i0g\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们不了解让出租车司机、工匠、医生或航空公司飞行员完成他们的工作的神经机制，更不了解用来寻找松露的狗如何挖掘出芬芳的“黑色钻石”，但我们相信他（它）们。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">为什么要对一台反应更快、不知疲倦、从不分心的机器提出更高的要求呢？当你可以证明它比人类更可靠时，为什么还要对它产生怀疑呢？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mn71tj9h1pxs\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">人工智能系统每天做出数万亿个决策，其中大多数都与查找、分类和过滤信息以及一些稍显无聊的应用程序有关，例如应用于照片和视频的效果。你是否真的愿意花时间和精力来详细了解它们？人工智能的工作能够带来令人满意的效果，这不就够了吗？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mn71tj9h12sm\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">而且使用没有深入了解其运行机制的系统是一种常见的现象。许多常用药物都是通过反复试错获得的，而我们对其作用机制了解甚少。比如，锂通常被用于治疗躁狂抑郁症，但它的作用机制至今仍是一个谜。我们熟悉的且在日常生活中不可被替代的阿司匹林是有史以来使用最广泛的药物，它于1897年首次稳定合成，可是直到1971年我们才明确其作用机制。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mn71tj9h13bg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">当我们无法完全说明系统的行为时，那么其市场流通就必须经过测试过程，测试的协议是受控且开放的，例如在药品进入市场之前进行的临床测试，或者用于新飞机的合格认证程序。对于做出关键决策的人工智能系统也必须如此。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mn71tj9h1ax6\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">另一个问题：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">投入实际应用的人工智能是否必须100%可靠？没有必要。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">同样的道理，为什么对人工智能的要求比对其他决策辅助系统的要求更高？医学每天都在使用的测试系统，其可靠性并非完美无缺，但我们不会质疑其有效性。例如，疾病的检测始终存在一定比例的假阳性和一定比例的假阴性，并且必须在两者之间进行权衡。如果对检测结果有任何疑问，医生将无法下诊断。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mn71tj9h1ach\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">既然如此，那为什么要对人工智能有更多的苛求呢？我的朋友莱昂·博图始终认为，现代社会产生的数据量与存储方式或网络速度一样，都在以相同的速度呈指数级增长。但是，人类处理这些信息的能力并没有如此迅速的增长，在某些时候，人类的大多数知识将由机器从数据中提取并存储。利用机器学习系统我们总可以轻松提出建议，无论建议的程度是深还是浅。我们需要做的是进行灵敏度分析，以便找到能够改变决策的最小输入干扰。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mn71tj9hk74\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">几个世纪以来，人类已经习惯自己的生理和心理能力被其他工具超越了：打磨过的石头和刀具比牙齿更坚硬；耕畜、拖拉机和挖掘机比我们的体力更强；马、汽车、飞机比我们的双脚移动得更快；计算机的计算速度比人脑更快。技术发现提升了我们自身的能力，机器智能也将延展人类智能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mn71tj9h1sjm\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">就像其他技术革新的时代一样，人工智能正在颠覆我们的时代。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">于我而言，我相信人工智能具备大大改善我们生活的能力，但我也相信它有制造问题的能力。对认识自我的渴望驱动着我们对机器智能的探索与追寻，对人工智能的研究和对人脑的研究相辅相成。因此，人工智能也是未来几十年我们要面临的一项巨大的科学技术挑战。</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mn71uak6rz5\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <div style=\"\">\n     <div data-tools=\"新媒体排版\" data-id=\"2200514\" data-style-type=\"undefined\" data-xmt-x1=\"621.5\" data-xmt-y1=\"4990.734375\" data-xmt-x2=\"1298.5\" data-xmt-y2=\"5122.734375\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div data-xmt-x1=\"621.5\" data-xmt-y1=\"4990.734375\" data-xmt-x2=\"1298.5\" data-xmt-y2=\"5122.734375\" style=\"border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div data-xmt-x1=\"621.5\" data-xmt-y1=\"4990.734375\" data-xmt-x2=\"1276.5\" data-xmt-y2=\"5106.734375\" style=\"padding: 8px;border-left: 6px solid rgb(169, 29, 6);line-height: 1.4;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(169, 29, 6);border-right-color: rgb(169, 29, 6);border-bottom-color: rgb(169, 29, 6);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mn71ue1zvae\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n        <p data-xmt-x1=\"635.5\" data-xmt-y1=\"4998.734375\" data-xmt-x2=\"1290.5\" data-xmt-y2=\"5017.734375\" style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: inherit;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mn71ue1f3d9\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">杨立昆（Yann LeCun） | 文</span></span></p>\n        <p data-xmt-x1=\"635.5\" data-xmt-y1=\"5017.734375\" data-xmt-x2=\"1290.5\" data-xmt-y2=\"5093.734375\" style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mn71ue1f10oj\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">杨立昆是图灵奖得主、Meta首席人工智能科学家。</span></p>\n        <p data-xmt-x1=\"635.5\" data-xmt-y1=\"5093.734375\" data-xmt-x2=\"1290.5\" data-xmt-y2=\"5114.734375\" style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mn71ue1f6k3\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">内容发布于杨立昆《科学之路》一书，本文有编辑删减。</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);white-space-collapse:collapse;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px 12px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;width: 676.997px;\">\n    <div data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;flex-direction: column;width: 653.003px;\">\n     <div data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);align-self:flex-start;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px -14px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;border-width:1px;border-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box !important;border-style:solid;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <div data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"padding:0px 7px;margin:0px;border-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;transform:translate(-3px, -3px);max-width:100%;border-width:1px;border-style:solid;height:24px;\">\n       <p data-mid=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;clear:both;font-size:14px;min-height:1em;line-height:24px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">The Thinker&nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 16px 18px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);width: 653.003px;\">\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);padding:0px;margin:5px 0px 8px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;font-family:PingFangSC-Regular, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;line-height:2em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 时代，我们更加需要能够穿越学科边界、连接思想与现实、在长期视角中讨论技术意义的思考者。The Thinker 内容共创计划应运而生，希望在加速变化的时代，保持判断力，保留复杂性，为关于科技与社会的公共讨论提供理性的洞见。The Thinker 共创的内容将面向企业决策者、科研人员、政策与产业观察者等读者群体，形成长期可积累、可引用的思想内容。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);padding:0px;margin:5px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;font-family:PingFangSC-Regular, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;line-height:2em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">欢迎向The Thinker专栏投稿，</span><span leaf=\"\">参与AI时代的公共讨论。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);padding:0px;margin:5px 0px 0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-size:14px;font-family:PingFangSC-Regular, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;;line-height:2em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">投稿邮箱：</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">thethinker@citicpub.com</span></span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "图灵奖得主杨立昆从通用技术视角深度剖析了 AI 对经济与社会的重塑，指出 AI 将延伸人类智能而非取代，并主张通过严格的测试协议而非过度追求黑匣子可解释性来治理 AI。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "图灵奖得主杨立昆从通用技术视角深度剖析了 AI 对经济与社会的重塑，指出 AI 将延伸人类智能而非取代，并主张通过严格的测试协议而非过度追求黑匣子可解释性来治理 AI。",
  "summary": "本文摘自图灵奖得主杨立昆（Yann LeCun）的著作《科学之路》，探讨了 AI 作为「通用技术」对社会经济的深远影响。杨立昆认为，AI 的发展将如同蒸汽机和电力一样引发职业更替，但人类将通过适应和再培训完成转型。他强调，AI 无法替代的创造力、人际交往及独特体验将变得更具价值。针对 AI 的「黑匣子」争议，他指出人类对复杂生物系统（如人脑、药物机制）的信任无需完全理解其内部机制，因此 AI 的治理应侧重于类似医药行业的严格测试协议，而非苛求完全的可解释性。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 是继蒸汽机、电力之后的又一「通用技术」。",
      "explanation": "AI 将深刻改变经济生活，虽然会引发职业更替，但历史经验表明人类有能力通过适应和培训来应对这种变革，不必过度恐慌。"
    },
    {
      "point": "创造力与人际互动将成为 AI 时代的核心价值。",
      "explanation": "随着自动化降低大众化产品的成本，那些 AI 无法参与竞争的、具有独特体验和感性价值的职业（如艺术、健康、教育）将变得更有价值。"
    },
    {
      "point": "重新审视 AI 的「黑匣子」问题与治理标准。",
      "explanation": "既然我们信任无法完全理解的生物智能和药物机制，就不应苛求 AI 必须 100% 可解释，而应建立类似临床测试的严格治理协议，以确保其可靠性。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "人工智能及其应用无法参与竞争的东西会变得更有价值，这是已经得到证明的人类经验。",
    "我们不了解让出租车司机、工匠、医生或航空公司飞行员完成他们的工作的神经机制……但我们相信他（它）们。为什么要对一台反应更快、不知疲倦、从不分心的机器提出更高的要求呢？",
    "技术发现提升了我们自身的能力，机器智能也将延展人类智能。"
  ],
